<p>system’s huge database of 800 to 1,200 questions and answers enables it to provide prompt and insightful answers. The Forever Project serves as an example of how SCA applications might help students and people or characters in historical and cultural contexts establish a natural and engaging relationship. (Kulkarni et al, 2020)</p>
</div>
